      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Addressing Attendance Concerns\n\nDear [Employee's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to address a matter that has come to our attention regarding your recent attendance at work. Over the past two weeks, we have noticed that you have been arriving approximately 15 minutes late to your shifts. While we understand that unforeseen circumstances can sometimes cause delays, consistent tardiness is impacting the efficiency of our morning handover process.\n\nAs a valued member of our team, we rely on each employee to adhere to the scheduled start times to ensure a smooth and organized workflow. Your punctuality is crucial to maintaining the high standards of our logistics operations. We kindly request that you make a concerted effort to arrive on time for your shifts moving forward.\n\nWe appreciate your understanding and cooperation in this matter. Should you have any concerns or require assistance, please do not hesitate to reach out to your supervisor or the HR department. We are here to support you and help address any underlying issues that may be contributing to this situation.\n\nThank you for your attention to this important matter.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]  \n[Your Position]  \n[Company Name]  \n[Contact Information]",
      "source": "target",
